<topic id="file-compare-toolbar">
  <title>Toolbar and Contextual Menu Actions of the Compare Files Tool</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Compare Files tool<indexterm>Toolbar</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_ucv_bgk_54b">The toolbar of the <uicontrol>Compare Files</uicontrol> tool contains operations that can be
      performed on the source and target files or XML fragments. Many of the actions are also
      available in the contextual menu.</p>
    <p id="p_vcv_bgk_54b">
      <fig id="fig_wcv_bgk_54b">
        <title>Compare Toolbar</title>
        <image href="../img/sa_compare_files_toolbar.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p id="p_xcv_bgk_54b">The following actions are available:</p>
    <p id="p_ycv_bgk_54b">
      <dl id="dl_zcv_bgk_54b">
        <dlentry id="dlentry_adv_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Algorithm</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>This drop-down menu allows you to select one of the following diff algorithms
            (depending on whether it is a two-way or three-way comparison):<ul
              conkeyref="reusables-tools/algorithm-ul" id="ul_bdv_bgk_54b">
              <li id="li_cdv_bgk_54b"/>
            </ul></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_ddv_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/OptionsShortcut16.png"/>Diff Options</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Opens the <xref href="preferences-diff-files.dita"
              product="author developer editor json"><uicontrol>Files Comparison</uicontrol>
              preferences page</xref><ph product="svnClient"><uicontrol>Files Comparison</uicontrol>
              preferences page</ph> where you can configure various options.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-tools/three-way-comparison-dlentry" id="dlentry_edv_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-perform-files-diff" id="dlentry_fdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_gdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DiffSynchronizeScroll20.png" id="image_ygw_yph_tc"
                placement="inline"/>Synchronized scrolling </uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Toggles synchronized scrolling on or off so that a selected difference can be seen on
            both sides of the application window. This option is on by default.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_hdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DiffIgnoreWhitespaces20.png" id="image_gmn_wk3_tc"
                placement="inline"/>Ignore Whitespaces</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Enables or disables the whitespace ignoring feature. Ignoring whitespace means that
            before performing the comparison, the application normalizes the content and trims its
            leading and trailing whitespaces.<ph product="author editor json"> This option is not
              available when in the <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> comparison mode.</ph></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="format_indent_files">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DiffPrettyPrint20.png"/>Format and Indent Both
              Files</uicontrol> (<uicontrol conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/ctrl_shift_p"
            />)</dt>
          <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-format-indent-ph"/><ph product="author editor">
              This option is not available when in the <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> comparison
              mode.</ph><note conkeyref="reusables-tools/format-indent-note" id="note_idv_bgk_54b"
            /></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="tags-display-mode" product="author editor">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/TagsDisplayMode24.png"/>Tags Display
            Mode</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Allows you to select the amount of markup to be displayed in the <xref
              href="file-comparison.dita#file-comparison/author_visual_mode"
                ><uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> visual comparison mode</xref>. You can choose
            between: <uicontrol><image href="../img/FullTagsWithAttrs16.png" id="image_gmv_lrm_wr"/>
              Full Tags with Attributes</uicontrol>, <uicontrol><image href="../img/FullTags16.png"
                id="image_y33_mrm_wr"/> Full Tags</uicontrol>, <uicontrol><image
                href="../img/BlockTags16.png" id="image_rcr_mrm_wr"/> Block Tags</uicontrol>,
                <uicontrol><image href="../img/BlockTagsWithoutNames16.png"/>Block Tags without
              Element Names</uicontrol>, <uicontrol><image href="../img/InlineTags16.png"
                id="image_usz_mrm_wr"/> Inline Tags</uicontrol>, <uicontrol><image
                href="../img/PartialTags16.png" id="image_qsh_nrm_wr"/> Partial Tags</uicontrol>, or
                <uicontrol><image href="../img/NoTags16.png" id="image_ucq_nrm_wr"/> No
              Tags</uicontrol>.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_jdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DiffCopyRightToLeft20.png" id="image_3hq_4k3_tc"
                placement="inline"/>Copy Change from Right to Left</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-copy-right-left"/></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_kdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DiffCopyAllRightToLeft20.png" id="image_svr_pk3_tc"
                placement="inline"/>Copy All Changes from Right to Left</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-copy-all-right-left-ph"/></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-next-block-changes" id="dlentry_ldv_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-previous-block-changes" id="dlentry_mdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-next-change" id="dlentry_ndv_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-previous-change" id="dlentry_odv_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_pdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DiffCopyAllLeftToRight20.png" placement="inline"/>Copy
              All Changes from Left to Right</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-copy-all-left-right-ph"/></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_qdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DiffCopyLeftToRight20.png" id="image_n2r_nk3_tc"
                placement="inline"/>Copy Change from Left to Right</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-tools/files-copy-left-right-ph"/></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-tools/ignore-nodes-by-xpath" id="dlentry_rdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-tools/files_first_change" id="dlentry_sdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_tdv_bgk_54b">
          <dt><uicontrol>Base</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Available for <xref href="file-comparison.dita#file-comparison/threeway_comparisons"
              >three-way comparisons</xref>. It is the base file that will be compared with the
            files opened in the left and right editors. You can specify the path to the file by
            using the text field, its history drop-down, or the browsing actions in the
                <uicontrol><image href="../img/BrowseDrop.png"/>Browse</uicontrol> drop-down
            menu.</dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_udv_bgk_54b">
          <dt>Left-Side (Source) File</dt>
          <dd>You can specify the path to the file to be compared on the left side (source) by using
            the text field, its history drop-down, or the browsing actions in the <uicontrol><image
                href="../img/BrowseDrop.png"/>Browse</uicontrol> drop-down menu.</dd>
          <dd>
            <p id="p_vdv_bgk_54b">
              <dl id="dl_wdv_bgk_54b">
                <dlentry id="dlentry_xdv_bgk_54b">
                  <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DiffSave16.gif"/>Save</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Saves the changes made in the source (left-side) file.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry id="dlentry_ydv_bgk_54b">
                  <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Refresh16.png"/>Reload</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Reloads the source (left-side) file.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry id="dlentry_zdv_bgk_54b">
                  <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Close12.png"/>Close</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Closes the source (left-side) file.</dd>
                </dlentry>
              </dl>
            </p>
          </dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry id="dlentry_a2v_bgk_54b">
          <dt>Right-Side (Target) File</dt>
          <dd><ph>You can specify the path to the file to be compared on the right side (target) by
              using the text field, its history drop-down, or the browsing actions in the
                  <uicontrol><image href="../img/BrowseDrop.png"/>Browse</uicontrol> drop-down
              menu.</ph></dd>
          <dd>
            <p id="p_b2v_bgk_54b">
              <dl id="dl_c2v_bgk_54b">
                <dlentry id="dlentry_d2v_bgk_54b">
                  <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DiffSave16.gif"/>Save</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Saves the target (right-side) file.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry id="dlentry_e2v_bgk_54b">
                  <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Refresh16.png"/>Reload</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Reloads the target (right-side) file.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry id="dlentry_f2v_bgk_54b">
                  <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Close12.png"/>Close</uicontrol></dt>
                  <dd>Closes the target (right-side) file.</dd>
                </dlentry>
              </dl>
            </p>
          </dd>
        </dlentry>
      </dl>
    </p>
  </body>
